headline: AppDirect Nears $1B in Gross Annual Recurring Revenue With a Bold Vision for B2B Commerce, Adds CrowdStrike Executive to Its Board of Directors
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, August 21, 2025--AppDirect, the world's leading B2B commerce platform, today announced the expansion of its board of directors with the addition of Burt Podbere, CFO at CrowdStrike. AppDirect anticipates crossing the $1 billion threshold in gross annual recurring revenue over the next 18-24 months.
